{"tid":1134332,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Cyberpunk]有冇人有玩Tales of the Neon Sea","createTime":"2019-05-01T17:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T08:39:35.000Z","uid":3296,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8e14abd9f2a5b56ce8cc06d170fa8af7a2d881f0","tid":1134332,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rupV5Jb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrupV5Jb.png&h=6710f509&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCzKY3m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCzKY3m.png&h=99ad7f08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMvx7WH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMvx7WH.png&h=659ae3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年關注左一大堆tba嘅cyberpunk game，今年終於出左好多，除左呢隻其實仲有katana zero, re legion, burning daylight<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻係Cyberpunk嘅解謎game<br />\n主角係偵探要去查案，目前得頭3章，製作團隊話秋季會免費更新埋剩低嘅<br />\n<br />\n個人就卡關卡左13個鐘，依家玩到差唔多完仲卡緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd謎我感覺唔算好重複但部份好濕鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />提示唔係好夠要自己摸好耐、撞出黎<br />\n<br />\n但畫面呢隻真係冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pixel+cyberpunk簡直係絕配<br />\n角色插圖都係非常靚，除此之外仲有好多好多貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你仲可以用貓嘅視角去探索、溝貓女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咁多其實想睇下有冇人爆左機教我過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e4cb4004706bec36fa98348c9905f6e10c2d40","tid":1134332,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5488b166040b87d9d019f4fae0fb50a6e12158","tid":1134332,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc353eddb3d7d19374058901dba930313f2b9ccb","tid":1134332,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"無玩，但係比你提醒左我要等呢隻野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/612400/The_Last_Night/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F612400%2FThe_Last_Night%2F&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=0679c407\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/612400/The_Last_Night/</a>"},{"pid":"12ea673c7f2650fecdc6ef9fcbf2373f63d6e34a","tid":1134332,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc353eddb3d7d19374058901dba930313f2b9ccb","tid":1134332,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"無玩，但係比你提醒左我要等呢隻野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/612400/The_Last_Night/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F612400%2FThe_Last_Night%2F&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=0679c407\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/612400/The_Last_Night/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"呢隻連日期都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ddc5a99d0fa9ab4f38e7097e7a28e770f627c01","tid":1134332,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8871b83f10c5246745577a8d44f309ef25ff1158","tid":1134332,"uid":5320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor